            "title": "A股午後疲弱   AI概念逆市升  滬股一周跌0.4%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">A股午後跌幅輕微擴大，AI應用股逆市齊升，兩市合計成交11189.75億元(人民幣‧下同)。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240307_FI_source-ap_AShare-11.png.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240307_FI_source-ap_AShare-11.png.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滬綜指全日收報3351，跌22點或0.67%，今早開報3372點，跌1點或0.03%﹐早段最高見3375，升2點或0.06%，其後拾級而下，午後低見3346，跌27點或0.8%，全日成交4688.08億元。滬股一周累跌0.4%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">深成指全日報10607，跌60點或0.57%，今早開報10658，跌10點或0.09%。最高見10688，升20點或0.19%，午後見10593，跌75點或0.7%，為全日低位，全日成交6501.67億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滬深300全日報3915，跌17點或0.44%，今早開報3930點，跌2點或0.05%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">創業板指數全日報2128點，跌16點或0.79%，今早開報2145點，跌5點0.23%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">AI應用方向午後齊漲，Sora概念領升，AI醫療跟漲。果麥文化(301052.SZ)升20%，報33.42元封板，中廣天擇(603721.SH)升3.67%，報26.73元 ; 開普雲(688228.SH)升3.47%，報59.7元。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14812172-a%e8%82%a1%e5%8d%88%e5%be%8c%e7%96%b2%e5%bc%b1-ai%e6%a6%82%e5%bf%b5%e9%80%86%e5%b8%82%e5%8d%87-%e6%bb%ac%e8%82%a1%e4%b8%80%e5%91%a8%e8%b7%8c0-4",
