            "title": "中升純利跌近36%末期息0.678元  午後股價持平",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">中升控股(00881)公布，截至去年底止全年純利32.12億元(人民幣‧下同)，按年跌35.99%；每股盈利1.35元；派末期息每股0.678港元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">期內，營業額1681.24億元，跌6.23%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">中升午後升0.57%，報14.16元。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14811850-%e4%b8%ad%e5%8d%87%e7%b4%94%e5%88%a9%e8%b7%8c%e8%bf%9136%e6%9c%ab%e6%9c%9f%e6%81%af0-678%e5%85%83-%e5%8d%88%e5%be%8c%e8%82%a1%e5%83%b9%e6%8c%81%e5%b9%b3",
